{"tid":426193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"員工過勞自殺 日本電通被罰50萬日圓","createTime":"2017-10-06T11:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T01:10:28.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b58489f44bc040458cbbc2be62ccfe879b749d9c","tid":426193,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpVqJEog.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpVqJEog.jpg&h=bc14c522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">過勞自殺的電通前員工高橋茉莉之母與律師。（美聯社）</span><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日本最大廣告公司電通因常態讓自家員工超時加班、去年甚至導致員工壓力過大自殺身亡，今天被日本法院裁定違反勞動基準法，罰款50萬日圓（約台幣13萬4600元）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phplfbTJJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phplfbTJJ.jpg&h=a7947e77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">日本最大的廣告公司電通，員工長時間過勞加班為常態。（路透）</span><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，電通24歲的女職員高橋茉莉因過度勞動患上嚴重抑鬱症，2015年聖誕節時於公司陽台跳樓輕生。該案以過勞自殺方向偵辦，偵查時為非公開、但判決時於公開法庭審理，高橋的母親也在現場聆聽宣判。<br />\n<br />\n面對電通的山本社長，法官菊地努表示：「發生這種讓員工於工作外時間違法過度勞動、導致尊貴生命消亡的悲慘事件，我們不能就這樣忽視。」並說電通做為業界的大型代表公司之一，改善公司勞動環境的進程將被全社會所關注，盼他們能好好承擔相應之社會責任。<br />\n<br />\n判決後受訪的山本社長表示會「嚴肅地接受判決結果，深刻反省」，將努力改革公司制度、遵循法律以杜絕過勞狀況。此外他也對過世的職員高橋茉莉感到非常抱歉，並於經過高橋母親坐著的旁聽席時，彎腰對她深深一鞠躬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2215522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2215522&d=DKpFC8K9Iqunn6gZfZiHKmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=1c532fff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2215522&h=baee3f86\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2215522</a><br />\n<br />\n嘩 50萬日圓 咩罰咁多呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b96564dd561f064d9ce1342871622474744736","tid":426193,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:44:44.000Z","msg":"嘩～～好大阻嚇力喎<br />\n<br />\n五十萬円<br />\n<br />\n美金都唔多啦"},{"pid":"087bca43a7d8bbd925fc1f3cf30fd9c5460ff9eb","tid":426193,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:47:42.000Z","msg":"50萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4a88a272559f21f5424c9cdbbb75113b400157","tid":426193,"uid":15880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:49:08.000Z","msg":"人命仲賤過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c22a783ea3d8dac968da2ffc0f1ba9ac5333a2","tid":426193,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20161008/640_fccddc9814fb0dda95d8a95c54ed786a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161008%2F640_fccddc9814fb0dda95d8a95c54ed786a.jpg&h=468efb7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8191fb82f2c4af7c5df9957c99607eef3d0e49","tid":426193,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:51:10.000Z","msg":"三萬五收買人命"},{"pid":"ccfe4d80c2711edc728d2942725530fd1c663dd2","tid":426193,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:51:56.000Z","msg":"出多咗一兩期糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f551e4f11bc8cde196503f68495858307cebe129","tid":426193,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:55:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff552b6f64575ed525dade48e08c31ae99793002","tid":426193,"uid":103405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T12:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/as